{"tid":1381512,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［銳變］憤怒過後見到警犬要笑","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:34:46.000Z","uid":23378,"like":472,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c7eb1ae65a4abaf091e066b2c68b3476795af6bf","tid":1381512,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"笑，可以係恥笑，可以係嘲笑。佢唔知你笑佢咩架，但已經可以令人不能自已。<br />\n<br />\n人好奇怪，若過一個人好憎自己，我地好識得唔理佢，忽視佢。<br />\n<br />\n過去一個月班狗比人屌老婆屌老母都無曬反應，我地係街見到指住黎屌仲有機會比佢反過黎入我地乜乜物物。<br />\n<br />\n不如轉下新玩法，見到嘅時候，唔洗指罵唔洗鬧，輕輕笑佢，望實黎笑，笑到佢心寒，笑到佢唔自在就得。<br />\n<br />\n笑比大大聲屌黎得更有力，無聲勝有聲。"},{"pid":"f64a5d4b421083656e89d092ebf72556feea30f1","tid":1381512,"uid":153245,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"自從6月見親警犬都望住佢哋陰陰嘴笑<br />\n<br />\n笑到佢哋無顏面對"},{"pid":"63605fd50d971e177da0192797f15bf5eada3693","tid":1381512,"uid":23378,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"f64a5d4b421083656e89d092ebf72556feea30f1","tid":1381512,"uid":153245,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"自從6月見親警犬都望住佢哋陰陰嘴笑<br />\n<br />\n笑到佢哋無顏面對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"啱 笑仲好 陰陰濕濕佢心理壓力仲大"},{"pid":"7cfafe03b689d403017325df04fb2680c6d5378a","tid":1381512,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"843f68a827ea89e1f328553dc5e6f853de3b3732","tid":1381512,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"4ffc063a7a1b636d409f38ef7536718893bebaf3","tid":1381512,"uid":23378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"沉"},{"pid":"578c421719b9bf9581762aaa24dc5e8e5c64cb14","tid":1381512,"uid":157138,"like":111,"dislike":0,"score":111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3de4e4g.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai